<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about-section" id="about">
  <div class="about-grid reveal">
    <div class="about-img">🔬</div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-tag">// About Our Lab</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Advancing Science for Humanity</h2>
      <p>The Electrochemistry and Catalysis Research Laboratory (ECRL) at Shahjalal University of Science and Technology (SUST) is dedicated to frontier research in electrochemical energy conversion, catalysis, and related fields.</p>
      <p>Our interdisciplinary team works at the intersection of chemistry, materials science, and engineering, focusing on developing sustainable solutions for energy storage, environmental remediation, and industrial catalysis.</p>
      <p>Since its inception, ECRL has produced internationally recognized research with over 3,200 citations, contributing significantly to the global scientific community.</p>
      <a href="#team" class="about-btn">Meet Our Team →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- RESEARCH -->
<section class="research-section" id="research">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-tag">// Research Focus</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Our Research Areas</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">We conduct cutting-edge research across multiple disciplines, pushing the boundaries of electrochemistry and catalysis science.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="research-grid reveal">
    <div class="research-card">
      <div class="r-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="r-title">Electrocatalysis</div>
      <p class="r-desc">Development of novel electrocatalysts for oxygen reduction, hydrogen evolution, and CO₂ reduction reactions for fuel cells and electrolyzers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="research-card">
      <div class="r-icon">🔋</div>
      <div class="r-title">Energy Storage</div>
      <p class="r-desc">Advanced electrode materials and electrolytes for lithium-ion, sodium-ion, and supercapacitor systems with enhanced performance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="research-card">
      <div class="r-icon">🌿</div>
      <div class="r-title">Green Catalysis</div>
      <p class="r-desc">Sustainable catalytic processes for biomass conversion, organic synthesis, and industrial applications with reduced environmental impact.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="research-card">
      <div class="r-icon">💧</div>
      <div class="r-title">Water Treatment</div>
      <p class="r-desc">Electrochemical and photocatalytic methods for degradation of pollutants, heavy metal removal, and water purification technologies.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="research-card">
      <div class="r-icon">🧪</div>
      <div class="r-title">Corrosion Science</div>
      <p class="r-desc">Investigation of corrosion mechanisms and development of protective coatings and inhibitors for metals and alloys in aggressive environments.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="research-card">
      <div class="r-icon">🔬</div>
      <div class="r-title">Nanomaterials</div>
      <p class="r-desc">Synthesis and characterization of nanostructured materials for catalytic and electrochemical applications with controlled morphology.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROFESSOR -->
<section class="about-section" id="professor">
  <div class="about-grid reveal">
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-tag">// Principal Investigator</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Prof. Dr. Md. Abul Hasnat</h2>
      <p>Professor of Chemistry at SUST, Prof. Dr. Hasnat leads the Electrochemistry and Catalysis Research Laboratory with over two decades of experience in the field.</p>
      <p>His research interests span electrocatalysis, corrosion science, and environmental electrochemistry. He has published over 128 articles in prestigious international journals and received numerous awards for his contributions to science.</p>
      <p>With an H-index of 32 and over 3,200 citations, Prof. Hasnat is among the most cited researchers in Bangladesh in the field of chemistry.</p>
      <a href="#publications" class="about-btn">View Publications →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="about-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f4ec, #d0e8d6); font-size: 5rem;">👨‍🔬</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PUBLICATIONS -->
<section class="pubs-section" id="publications">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-tag">// Recent Work</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Featured Publications</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">A selection of our most impactful peer-reviewed research published in leading international journals.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pub-list reveal">
    <div class="pub-item">
      <span class="pub-year">2024</span>
      <div>
        <div class="pub-title">Efficient Electrocatalytic Reduction of CO₂ on Bimetallic Cu-Zn Nanostructures for Formate Production</div>
        <div class="pub-authors">M.A. Hasnat, R. Ahmed, S. Islam · ECRL, SUST</div>
      </div>
      <span class="pub-venue">ACS Catalysis</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pub-item">
      <span class="pub-year">2024</span>
      <div>
        <div class="pub-title">Nitrogen-Doped Carbon Supported Iron Oxide for Oxygen Reduction in Alkaline Media</div>
        <div class="pub-authors">F. Khatun, M.A. Hasnat, N. Roy · ECRL, SUST</div>
      </div>
      <span class="pub-venue">J. Phys. Chem. C</span>
